<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Protect" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Protect,</orth> 1) to guard, to defend, to shield: <bibl n="shak. tn 2.4.75" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. II, 4, 75</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.3.9" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 3, 9</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.3.5" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 3, 5</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.3.5" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 3, 5</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 2.1.54" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 54</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 3.2.276" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 III, 2, 276</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 5.1.142" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 142</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 5.4.11" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 4, 11</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 1.4.227" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. I, 4, 227</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 1.1.128" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 1, 128</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 4.2.126" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 126</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 1.4.97" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. I, 4, 97</bibl>. With <cit><quote>from:</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 4.1.20" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 1, 20</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. per 2.1.135" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. II, 1, 135</bibl>.<lb />2) to guard, to superintend, to tend: <cit><quote>must you p. my lady here?</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 2.4.79" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B II, 4, 79</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>despite the bearward that --s the bear,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 5.1.210" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 210</bibl></cit>.
<lb />3) to be protector, to be regent for: <cit><quote>why should he then p. our sovereign,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.1.165" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 1, 165</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>why a king of years should be to be --ed like a child,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 2.3.29" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 3, 29</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the king had virtuous uncles to p. his grace,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 2.3.21" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 II, 3, 21</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>